my_game is a step by step from http://ruby4kids.com/ruby4kids
Based on gem Gosu http://www.libgosu.org/

Ruby4Kids PDF
	Presentation Classes and Objects:
	http://ruby4kids.com/ruby4kids/public/download/10
	Ruby Fundamentals:
	http://ruby4kids.com/ruby4kids/public/download/12

Control Keys:
Keyboard arrows left, up, right, down
Escape key to reset the game